com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto

Interface ILockSearchCriteria

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.INamedSearchCritieria, ISearchCriteria

    public interface ILockSearchCriteria
extends com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.INamedSearchCritieria, ISearchCriteria
    This interface defines the criteria that locks can match. Every criteria can either be set or unset (set to null). When multiple criteria are set the result is the conjunction of all the criteria.
    Since:
    0.7
